dialog.body: Hi, I'm interested in learning piano at Noteworthy. Can you tell me about the pricing for beginner classes?
Hello Jane, I'm Scott Wood from Noteworthy. I'll be happy to help you with that. Are you looking for private or group classes?
I'm thinking about private classes to start with.
Great choice, Jane. Our private beginner classes are $50 per session. How often would you like to schedule the classes?
I'd like to begin with once a week.
Perfect. So, that would be $200 per month for weekly sessions. Does that work for you?
Yes, that sounds good. How do I sign up?
You can sign up on our website or I can send you a link to register directly. Would you like the link, Jane?
A link would be perfect, thank you.
I've sent the registration link to your email. Let me know if there's anything else I can help with!
